---
title: Chris Collins – Full Stack Developer & Digital Designer based in Glasgow
description: Chris Collins is a Full Stack Developer & Digital Designer based in Glasgow, Scotland.
layout: base.njk

pagination:
    data: collections.log
    size: 100
    alias: log
---

<div class="container md:my-8 md:-mt-8">
    <div class="lg:flex items-center justify-between lg:text-center">
        <section class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-gray-600 dark-mode:text-gray-400 mb-1 leading-tight">Hello, I’m Chris</h1>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight mb-4 md:mb-6 font-bold">I design and build digital products, hike and take photos.</h2>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl sans-serif max-w-xl">I'm a Full Stack Developer & Digital Designer based in Glasgow, Scotland. At present I'm building web things at <a href="https://news.stv.tv" class="cool-link" target="_blank">STV News</a>.</p>
        </section>
    </div>


    <h2 class="text-xl mt-8 leading-tight  mb-6 font-semibold">Latest Walk Reports</h2>

    <ul class="my-8 flex -mx-4 scroll-snap scrolling-touch overflow-x-scroll">
        {% for hike in log %}
            {% if hike.url %}
                <li class="scroll-snap-child py-1 mb-4 sm:w-1/2 md:w-1/3 p-4" style="min-width: 260px;">
                    <a href="{{ hike.url | url }}" class="no-underline ">
                        <article class="h-full flex flex-col">
                            <img class="rounded-lg" src="{{ hike.url | url }}{{ hike.data.featured_image }}">
                            <div class="py-4">
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 tracking-wider font-bold uppercase flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <time>{{ hike.data.date | simpleDate }}</time>
                                    <span class="text-gray-600 opacity-50">{{ hike | readingTime }} read</span>
                                </div>
                                <h3 class="truncate item-end mb-0 mr-2 text-base font-bold">{{ hike.data.name }}</h3>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                    </a>
                </li>
            {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</div>